1
00:00:04,871 --> 00:00:06,906
You're thirty minutes late.

2
00:00:09,002 --> 00:00:10,503
I didn't even want to come.

3
00:00:11,778 --> 00:00:12,779
Why call me now?

4
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:14,680
What's this about?

5
00:00:17,584 --> 00:00:18,718
Look...

6
00:00:20,587 --> 00:00:22,355
Can we just bury the hatchet?

7
00:00:22,589 --> 00:00:25,258
Bury the hatchet?

8
00:00:28,361 --> 00:00:30,997
You mean about you poaching my talent?

9
00:00:31,765 --> 00:00:32,865
Or how you let Bai Xing...

10
00:00:32,866 --> 00:00:33,999
constantly get tangled up...

11
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:35,468
with our Hei Yan?

12
00:00:36,169 --> 00:00:37,169
Lin Bingchen.

13
00:00:37,570 --> 00:00:38,905
Let's just talk like adults.

14
00:00:40,907 --> 00:00:41,907
Like adults?

15
00:00:42,976 --> 00:00:43,676
You left without a word...

16
00:00:43,677 --> 00:00:44,878
back then.

17
00:00:45,612 --> 00:00:47,013
And now you want to talk?

18
00:00:48,681 --> 00:00:49,983
Fine. I'm all ears.

19
00:01:03,530 --> 00:01:04,930
You never drink.

20
00:01:04,931 --> 00:01:06,199
Why the sudden shot?

21
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,400
What?

22
00:01:09,035 --> 00:01:10,670
Is Hei Yan's contract almost up?

23
00:01:11,604 --> 00:01:12,884
Are you trying to poach him too?

24
00:01:13,273 --> 00:01:14,808
Is that really what you think of me?

25
00:01:15,208 --> 00:01:16,242
Yeah.

26
00:01:23,550 --> 00:01:24,550
What are you doing?

27
00:01:26,586 --> 00:01:28,254
I need some liquid courage.

28
00:01:53,213 --> 00:01:54,414
What do you want?

29
00:01:56,015 --> 00:01:57,851
Bai Xing wanted me to tell you...

30
00:01:58,384 --> 00:01:59,252
not to get in the way...

31
00:01:59,253 --> 00:02:01,020
of the two of them.

32
00:02:02,789 --> 00:02:03,857
Get in the way of what?

33
00:02:04,157 --> 00:02:05,725
What could I even do?

34
00:02:06,092 --> 00:02:07,894
Tell Bai Xing to come see me himself.

35
00:02:08,328 --> 00:02:09,796
Why are you doing his dirty work?

36
00:02:12,098 --> 00:02:14,067
It all started with me, didn't it?

37
00:02:17,971 --> 00:02:19,371
Stop drinking if you can't handle it.

38
00:02:19,372 --> 00:02:20,807
I can't say this if I'm sober.

39
00:02:23,676 --> 00:02:24,676
I'm sorry.

40
00:02:26,045 --> 00:02:27,280
Don't. I've already forgotten.

41
00:02:28,214 --> 00:02:30,750
No, I need to say it.

42
00:02:31,117 --> 00:02:32,485
I was such an idiot.

43
00:02:32,886 --> 00:02:34,386
I believed what people were saying...

44
00:02:34,387 --> 00:02:36,022
and that's why I broke up with you.

45
00:02:37,991 --> 00:02:39,058
You call that a breakup?

46
00:02:39,425 --> 00:02:40,193
You sent one text...

47
00:02:40,194 --> 00:02:41,627
said it wasn't working, and vanished.

48
00:02:41,628 --> 00:02:43,396
You didn't even give
me a chance to explain.

49
00:02:43,830 --> 00:02:45,297
That wasn't a breakup.

50
00:02:45,298 --> 00:02:46,566
You abandoned me.

51
00:02:47,167 --> 00:02:48,902
That's why I'm saying I was stupid!

52
00:02:49,369 --> 00:02:50,736
I listened to them...

53
00:02:50,761 --> 00:02:52,729
and I just ended it.

54
00:02:53,207 --> 00:02:54,716
[Unintelligible gay hysterics]

55
00:02:54,741 --> 00:02:55,375
I don't want both of us...

56
00:02:55,376 --> 00:02:56,775
to end up in the news tomorrow.

57
00:02:56,776 --> 00:02:57,809
But what else can I do?

58
00:02:57,810 --> 00:02:59,612
I just really wanted to say I'm sorry.

59
00:03:00,046 --> 00:03:01,980
I'm such a fool.

60
00:03:01,981 --> 00:03:03,916
They just kept talking...

61
00:03:03,917 --> 00:03:05,684
and I believed every word.

62
00:03:05,685 --> 00:03:06,952
They said all those things...

63
00:03:06,953 --> 00:03:08,521
and I just believed them.
